OL,6,FThe Minister for Sustainable Economic
OL,7,FDevelopment, Deputy Kirsten Morel,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The Council of Ministers has
OL,9,Fcommitted to transitioning to a living
OL,10,Fwage.
OL,12,F"To support employers through this
OL,13,Ftransition we've designed a package to
OL,14,Fhelp organisations invest in
OL,15,Fthemselves and help the Island move to
OL,16,Fa more productive and resilient
OL,17,Feconomy.
